---
---

<header class="relative w-full min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 md:px-0 py-16 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Image de fond avec blur -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover -z-20"
    style="background-image: url('/hero-bg.jpg'); background-position: center center;"
  ></div>
  <!-- Overlay clair pour lisibilité -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#F5EDE4]/70 backdrop-blur-sm -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-6 md:space-y-8 z-10 w-full">

    <span class="inline-flex flex-col items-center py-1.5 px-4 border border-[#D6CCC0] rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-[#767A55] bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm leading-relaxed">
      <span>Community Manager</span>
      <span>pour Artisans &amp; Indépendants</span>
    </span>

    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl text-[#2C2416] leading-tight tracking-tight">
      Votre savoir-faire<br />
      mérite d'être <span class="italic font-light text-[#8B3E22]">vu</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="max-w-sm md:max-w-xl mx-auto text-base md:text-xl text-[#2C2416]/70 font-light leading-relaxed">
      J'aide les artisans et indépendants à construire une présence Instagram qui attire de vrais clients — je m'occupe de tout.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
      <a
        href="#offres"
        class="group px-7 py-3.5 md:px-8 md:py-4 bg-[#8B3E22] text-[#F5EDE4] rounded-full hover:bg-[#6B2E1A] transition-colors duration-300 w-full sm:w-auto font-medium flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
      >
        Voir mes offres
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-right-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></iconify-icon>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://cal.com/claire-vigneron-k5okcq/30min?user=claire-vigneron-k5okcq&overlayCalendar=true"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="px-7 py-3.5 md:px-8 md:py-4 border border-[#D6CCC0] text-[#2C2416] rounded-full hover:bg-[#EDE6DB] transition-all duration-300 w-full sm:w-auto font-medium text-center bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-sm"
      >
        Réserver un appel gratuit
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</header>
